news.title: Bengaluru: CID arrests Mantri Developers' director, son after complaints from buyers
news.para: Several homebuyers had filed complaints with Subramanyapura police stating that they were cheated of money by the builders, who had lured them with attractive offers, misleading brochures and fake schemes.

news.title: Cash-strapped Ludhiana civic body revises property tax target to Rs 130 crore
news.para: Officials claimed that they expect to recover at least Rs 60 crore by the month-end, for which they were organising special camps in commercial areas and industrial units.

news.title: Haryana: Error in property tax ID? Submit complaints via NDC
news.para: The civic body has also decided to form a separate NDC cell to immediately resolve property IDs-related grievances.
